{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: "And, that's all of Mr. Hassen's words.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: "I still can't believe HQ would allow us to stay in Forsaken camps for a night...", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'They really are trying to use us as diplomatic envoys.', 4: '3'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'Miss Celica, will the Purifying Force still go after Watanabe?', 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 3: '1'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Hmph... What a convoluted world we live in.', 4: '3'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Heyo, Commandant. You get some nice sleep last night?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Where were you last night?', 4: '3'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "Just on patrol. They seem to think I'm part of the Gray Raven squad.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Ah whatever, we have a new mission, right?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Celica, tell us the details already!', 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 3: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: "You'll have to depart from Forsaken territory and go toward City 019 around 30km away from here.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Kamui... Did Chrome not give you a new mission?', 4: '2'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 3: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: "Your next mission isn't about tracking the Ascendants, but it's still dangerous—the location there is uninvestigated.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Celica', 3: 'Kamui, as part of the Strike Hawk squad, will also go there to search for any possible Ascendant traces.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 4: '1'}
{3: 'After a while...'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "Why's... Watanabe following us?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'City 019 is a nearby source of corruption and has been endangering the area.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'This is a life-or-death matter for the Forsaken, naturally, I have to be a part of this.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'Okay—City 019, underground shelter city. This is its entrance.', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "(Watanabe... He's not being straight with himself.)", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "(Watanabe's similar to Lee in this front.)", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: '(Hmm, well, maybe slightly different, still though...)', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "(I... don't think I can really tell...)", 4: '2'}
